# League DB

League DB is an API allowing players and fans of League of Legends to view different
kinds of information. All data will be in the JSON format.

## Champions [/api/champions]

### Get All Champions [GET]

Get information about every champion.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "name": "aatrox",
                "role": "top",
                "class": "skirmishers",
                "items": [
                    "bladeoftheruinedking",
                    "deathsdance",
                    ...
                ],
                "lore": "Aatrox is a legendary warrior...",
                "image": "https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/7.12.1/img/champion/Aatrox.png"
            },
            {
                "name": "ahri",
                "role": "mid",
                "class": "mages",
                "items": [
                    "morellonomicon",
                    "ludensecho",
                    ...
                ],
                "lore": "Unlike other foxes that roamed the woods of southern Ionia...",                
                "image": "https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/7.12.1/img/champion/Ahri.png"
            },
            ...
        ]

### Get A Champion By Name [GET /api/champions/{name}]

Get information about one champion by using a name parameter, which must contain only 
lowercase letters.

+ Parameters
    + name: draven

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "name": "draven",
                "role": "bot",
                "class": "marksmen",
                "items": [
                    "deathsdance",
                    "statikkshiv",
                    ...
                ],
                "lore": "Unlike his brother Darius,champ victory in battle was never enough for Draven...",
                "image": "https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/7.12.1/img/champion/Draven.png"
            }
        ]

