Get information about all the roles in the game.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "type": "bot",
                "champions":[
                    "draven",
                    "vayne",
                    ...
                ],
                "items": [
                    "infinityedge",
                    "phantomdancer",
                    ...
